  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Backend Office Admin",
  "description": "<p>The purpose of the role is to verify and consolidate public behaviour (eg Smoking, urinating, Spitting, Defecating ) / traffic infringements from CCTV footage for customers.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Scan, note down and verify any Public Behaviour/ Traffic infringements from the CCTV monitors</p></li><li><p>Validate all incoming Public Behaviour/ Traffic infringements and submit to BOS Team Lead.</p></li><li><p>Attend to enquiries regarding verification of Public Behaviour/ Traffic infringements and other related services</p></li><li><p>Report faulty cameras or breakdowns</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with Technical Support team on camera repairs and adjustments</p></li><li><p>Resolve all in scope enquiries and take appropriate escalation actions when required</p></li><li><p>Other duties as assigned</p></li><li><p>Comply with the company’s Safe work procedures at all times</p></li><li><p>Prepare violation report extracted from application<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Competence (Knowledge, Skills and Abilities):</strong></p><ul><li><p>Knowledge of Public Behaviour/ Traffic violation rules</p></li><li><p>Basic computer skills<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Able to converse well with customers on enquiries<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Education & Experience:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum ‘O’ Level or equivalent</p></li><li><p>Preferably with experience working with CCTV systems. Otherwise, training will be provided.<br /></p></li></ul><p>For personal data protection (PDP) related matters, pls refer to our PDP policy via corporate website at oconnors.co Personal Data Protection Policy.</p>",
